http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Thiruvananthapuram/Bank-strike-total/article13989757.ece

: The one-day strike called for the AIBEA-affiliated State Sector Banks Employees Association and the BEFI-affiliated SBT Staff Union against moves for merger of associate banks with the SBI hit the functioning of the bank on Friday.Leadership of the staff unions said the strike was total and reflected rejection of the merger move, sought to be implemented in the name of Career Progression Scheme, by the employees. The strike would ensure that SBT would remain an independent entity, which has been one of the main issues being raised by the employees, they claimed.